

This directory is for PlatformIO and MicroPython tests for the Mavlink Bridge project.

## How to Add Tests

- For PlatformIO (C++), add test files for your bridge logic, MAVLink parsing, and hardware drivers.
- For MicroPython, add test scripts to validate menu navigation, settings, and UDP-to-UART bridging.

## Example Tests

- See `test/test_main.cpp` for C++ examples.
- See `micropython/test_menu.py` for MicroPython menu tests (if present).

## Resources

- PlatformIO Unit Testing: https://docs.platformio.org/en/latest/advanced/unit-testing/index.html
- MicroPython testing: https://docs.micropython.org/en/latest/reference/unittest.html
